snippet: Anthony Davis tied his career high with 32 points, grabbed 17 rebounds and blocked six shots, and the New Orleans Pelicans erased a 16-point deficit to capture their third straight victory, 111-107 over the Denver Nuggets in overtime Sunday night....

headline.print_headline: Davis Leads Pelicans Past Nuggets, 111-107 in OT
headline.main: Davis Leads Pelicans Past Nuggets, 111-107 in OT

lead_paragraph: Anthony Davis tied his career high with 32 points, grabbed 17 rebounds and blocked six shots, and the New Orleans Pelicans erased a 16-point deficit to capture their third straight victory, 111-107 over the Denver Nuggets in overtime Sunday night.
